; Regression test for issue #857: -S in a balance report results in filename error (BZ#857)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/857
;
; The original bug was that using -S (short form of --sort) in a balance report
; caused a filename error instead of sorting. This is now fixed.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food        $10.00
    Expenses:Rent       $500.00
    Expenses:Gas         $50.00
    Assets:Checking    $-100.00
    Assets:Cash

; -S total (short form of --sort) should work without error in a balance report
test bal -S total
            $-560.00  Assets
            $-460.00    Cash
            $-100.00    Checking
             $560.00  Expenses
              $10.00    Food
              $50.00    Gas
             $500.00    Rent
--------------------
                   0
end test
